OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775837470
OL,3,CA landmark Scottish domestic abuse
OL,4,Csentencing gives victims hope
OL,6,FWarning: Distressing content
OL,8,FIt's taken a lot of steps and lives to
OL,9,Fget here, but for the first time,
OL,10,FScotland's legal system has recognised
OL,11,Fthe link between domestic abuse and
OL,12,Fsuicide.
OL,14,FThe landmark conviction of Lee Milne
OL,15,Ffor culpable homicide over the death
OL,16,Fof his wife, Kimberly, in Dundee in
OL,17,FJuly 2023, followed a trial at the
OL,18,FGlasgow High Court. Milne, 40, was
OL,19,Fjailed at the same court on Friday for
OL,20,Feight years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
