PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775837470
OL,3,CA landmark Scottish domestic abuse
OL,4,Csentencing gives victims hope
OL,6,FIt marks a significant shift in the
OL,7,FScottish justice system, recognising
OL,8,Fthat perpetrators of domestic violence
OL,9,Fcan be held to account when their
OL,10,Fabuse drives a victim to take their
OL,11,Fown life.
OL,13,FCampaigners and charities have long
OL,14,Fcalled for this recognition.
OL,16,FTheir cause for celebration comes at
OL,17,Fthe cost of tragedy and loss of life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
