PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775837470
OL,3,CA landmark Scottish domestic abuse
OL,4,Csentencing gives victims hope
OL,6,FIn 2023, after an argument with her
OL,7,Fhusband, Milne, 28-year-old Kimberly
OL,8,Fjumped to her death from a motorway
OL,9,Fbridge in Dundee.
OL,11,FCCTV footage showed the pair arguing,
OL,12,Fwith Milne trapping his wife against a
OL,13,Fwall. Passersby stopped to check that
OL,14,FKimberly was ok and described her as
OL,15,Fbeing "terrified".
OL,17,FThe High Court in Glasgow heard that
OL,18,FMilne subjected his wife to repeated
OL,19,Fviolence and controlling behaviour
OL,20,Fthroughout their relationship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775837470
OL,3,CA landmark Scottish domestic abuse
OL,4,Csentencing gives victims hope
OL,6,FKimberly's death and the circumstances
OL,7,Fleading up to her decision to take her
OL,8,Fown life confirm what many victims
OL,9,Fhave known for a long time.
OL,11,FNot all abuse takes place behind
OL,12,Fclosed doors. Until now, this hasn't
OL,13,Fbeen reflected in the justice system.
OL,15,FMilne denied culpable homicide and a
OL,16,Fseparate charge of domestic abuse. The
OL,17,Fruling is hugely significant and could
OL,18,Fset a legal precedent for cases that
OL,19,Ffollow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
