OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775837470
OL,3,CA landmark Scottish domestic abuse
OL,4,Csentencing gives victims hope
OL,6,FElsewhere in the UK, there's only ever
OL,7,Fbeen one case in England, where a man
OL,8,Fhas been convicted of killing their
OL,9,Fpartner by causing suicide. That was
OL,10,Falmost a decade ago, in 2017.
OL,12,FIt is estimated across the UK that
OL,13,Falmost 30 women attempt suicide every
OL,14,Fday as a result of domestic abuse.
OL,15,FEvery week, three women take their own
OL,16,Flives.
OL,18,FFrom April 1 2026, every death from
OL,19,Fsuicide in Scotland where domestic
OL,20,Fabuse is suspected will be reviewed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
