OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775837470
OL,3,CA landmark Scottish domestic abuse
OL,4,Csentencing gives victims hope
OL,6,FIt's part of The Criminal Justice
OL,7,FModernisation and Abusive Domestic
OL,8,FBehaviour Reviews (Scotland) Bill.
OL,10,FThis means justice, health, social
OL,11,Fcare, local government and third
OL,12,Fsector organisations will now work
OL,13,Ftogether to identify and agree on any
OL,14,Fareas for change and improvement so
OL,15,Ffurther deaths may be prevented.
OL,17,FFiona Drouet, whose daughter Emily
OL,18,Ftook her own life after being abused
OL,19,Fby her boyfriend in 2016, has led the
OL,20,Fcampaign in Scotland for the end of
OL,21,FGender Based Violence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775837470
OL,3,CA landmark Scottish domestic abuse
OL,4,Csentencing gives victims hope
OL,6,FDrouet said: "This sentencing is
OL,7,Fsignificant. Hopefully it leads to
OL,8,Fsome training, greater awareness in
OL,9,Fall of our services and our justice
OL,10,Fsystems to ensure that nobody falls
OL,11,Fthrough those cracks. We can't write
OL,12,Fthis off as just a suicide."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
