PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775837470
OL,3,CA landmark Scottish domestic abuse
OL,4,Csentencing gives victims hope
OL,6,FLaura Buchan, legal director for death
OL,7,Finvestigations in the Crown Office and
OL,8,FProcurator Fiscal Service, said: "This
OL,9,Fcase demonstrates that emotional and
OL,10,Fpsychological abuse can be as
OL,11,Fdangerous as physical abuse.
OL,13,F"We hope that this case raises
OL,14,Funderstanding amongst the public that
OL,15,Fvictims who may not realise that they
OL,16,Fare in a coercive or controlling
OL,17,Frelationship are confident they can
OL,18,Freport that abuse to the police and
OL,19,Fthat we as prosecutors will
OL,20,Finvestigate, prosecute and see abusers
OL,21,Fconvicted.
OL,26,@pD@bOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775837470
OL,3,CA landmark Scottish domestic abuse
OL,4,Csentencing gives victims hope
OL,6,F"Almost 70% of our business in the
OL,7,Fhigh courts (in Scotland) is made up
OL,8,Fof serious sexual offences and
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse."
OL,11,F"In 2024 to 2025, we received just
OL,12,Fover 30,000 charges of domestic abuse
OL,13,Freported to us and 85% are charges
OL,14,Fwhere violence is perpetrated against
OL,15,Fwomen by men."
OL,17,FDespite this landmark ruling, no
OL,18,Fsentence will bring Kimberly back or
OL,19,Fgive her family and friends closure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@PO]wD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
